<!-- 📘 CLAUDE.local.md is your PERSONAL, gitignored layer on top of CLAUDE.md. It loads the same
     way but never gets committed, so it's the right home for things that are true for YOU on YOUR
     machine but shouldn't be forced on the team. Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` to use it.
     (We ship a `.example` so the pattern is visible without committing a real local file.) -->

# Personal overrides (not committed)

## My setup
- I run the dev server on port 4000 (`npm run dev -- -p 4000`).
- My scratch notes for this project live in `~/notes/verdant.md` (don't read it unless I point you there).

## My preferences for this repo
- When you finish a change, show me the diff before committing.
- I like terse commit messages. No fluff.
